						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							I think those will never get major attention because they are not big usage things for the average user.   Something like GIMP however needs more attention as its functionally equal to Photoshop but its free and you do not depend on Adobe and its DRM.  Especially now that they want to push all their crap to &quot;The Cloud&quot; now,  Adobe is even less appealing.<br />
<br />
Blender also needs more attention IMHO,  It is a very capable modeling program that generally gets shrugged off because its not autodesk.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
